title: 2019 with Posh People | StreetSmart
description: In this video, Max Fosh explores the streets of London to interact with posh people and see how they react to his unconventional questions and antics.
summary: Max Fosh interviews posh people on the streets of London and engages in humorous conversations with them.
payoff: The humor in this video comes from the contrast between Max's laid-back and quirky personality and the posh people's reactions to his offbeat questions and behavior. It is amusing to see how they respond to his unconventional approach and how they try to maintain their composure in the face of his antics.
